3000-01-01  Nobody  <nobody@secretchronicles.de>

	* Version unreleased.
	* Feature: Added a working `PKGBUILD' file for ArchLinux.
	* Feature: Add new world hill graphics `Dune_2', `Dune_3',
	`Dune_big_1', `Dune_big_2', `Green_hill_1', `Green_hill_2',
	`Green_hill_big_1', `Green_hill_big_2' (forum contribution by
	David F. Fernández)
	* Feature: Added Doom Larry enemy and Larry graphics improvements (PR #460 by Chris Jacobsen, graphics by Bugsbane)
	* Fix: Fix some issues found by coverity (PR #455 by Tobias Markus)
	* Fix: Added scoring for Larries (PR #460 by Chris Jacobsen)
	* Misc: Added Travis CI config (PR #453 by Lauri Ojansivu)

